Package: textir  
Title:  Inverse Regression for Text Analysis  
Version: 2.0  
Date: 8/2013  
Author: Matt Taddy <taddy@chicagobooth.edu>  
Depends: R (>= 2.10), Matrix  
Suggests: MASS, Parallel  
Description:  A suite of tools for text mining and similar tasks.  
